channel.title: [Making] Making Free InvisionFree Forums for Servers
channel.description:
Hello Everyone,
Yes its me again, God of Ikiliki This time Im making InvisionFree Forums for Every Server if you want it. People keep asking or PMing me to make Forums for their servers, and I like to make them. You can choose the Skin you want. Here are Some Good sites you can find invisionfree skins on. You need to give me the link to the Topic/Page the skin codes are posted on. Note: If your note sure how they look like, InvisionFree Skin Codes Always Having: - CSS - Header & Body
[b]Here are a few sites you can find skins on:[/b] http://support.invisionfree.com/index.php?showforum=47 http://forums.ifskinzone.net (Has the Best Skins, Needs Registering) http://forums.zetastyles.com (Has the Best Skins, Needs Registering)
[b]When you don't know any skin I will add this Skin:[/b] http://z8.invisionfree.com/AutoSkin
The Form: [code]Your Server Name: Link to Logo (If you Got one): [Do not Post screenshots, just Logo's that are not too high!] IP: Port: You want a Front Page?: Yes/No Snow?: Yes/No Server Owner: Link to Skin Codes: [ Put -- If you dont know a good one or like the Auto Skin I add][/code]
Forums I Made: Http://z6.invisionfree.com/gods_fantasy Http://z10.invisionfree.com/kingshits_server Http://z8.invisionfree.com/smurfscape Http://z8.invisionfree.com/endlesspkerz Http://z8.invisionfree.com/svenscape http://z11.invisionfree.com/godsendscape (Gone, Don't know Why) http://z8.invisionfree.com/JavasBlades_Forums http://z8.invisionfree.com/Elite_PK
[b]Note:[/b] The Front Page is the Page you see when your opening the Forums If you dont want it you auto see the Forum to Post in! I will add at the Bottom of the Page Credits Do not Remove/change them, when you remove/change them I:
1.) Add you to the Official Mass Report List 2.) Contact my M8s of the InvisionFree Forums, I was a [u]Ex[/u] Mod on the Support Forums (I forgot my name when my old Pc Crashed)
[glow=red,2,300]So dont Remove or Change my Name to Your Name![/glow]
P.S Do not PM me to ask to make me One or if im done! Im Posting every forum that is done here! [br][size=1]Posted at: December 22, 2006, 01:36:54 PM[/size][hr]Added some examples
